author: CBS Dallas / Fort Worth
title: Viral Video: Local Pastor Sings Of His Love Of Biscuits
text:
Viral Video: Local Pastor Sings Of His Love Of Biscuits February 23, 2017 6:10 AM 
Follow CBSDFW.COM: Facebook | Twitter 
A video of a pastor from McKinney has gone viral…and it’s a video about true love. 
Pastor Fred Thomas sits in his car and sings of his love for his Whataburger honey butter chicken biscuit. 
Watch he sings “Something About This Biscuit”
